{"title":"跳石","authors":["管用和"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":1,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管用和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石竖溪中，可行走，曰跳石。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个一个逗号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点在水中——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"间间隔隔的桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断断续续的路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要一步一步地走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一步得落在实处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也别想取巧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——省掉一步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的的确确"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是句号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此岸到彼岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能停足"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为身后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不容你久久停顿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不能返身转去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只准一个意念："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过去！过去了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会真正领悟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条人生之路"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}